data.description: YOU'RE GOING TO LOVE LIVING HERE! From the large rocking chair front porch to the newly updated eat-in kitchen with BEAUTIFULLY redone cabinets to the back deck, there's plenty to love in this great home on this quiet cul-de-sac!! Master on main with two spacious secondary bedrooms upstairs and about 600SF with a finished bonus room that is currently used as an office. Basement also is stubbed for a bathroom.  Plenty of storage inside this house, but this sale also includes a 16X16 storage building with a U-shaped loft for even more storage!  Owners have spent Over $9,000 to add concrete to increase the parking area.   HOA fee is only $288 per year an includes use of clubhouse and swimming pool. Owner works from home so showings are appointment only with 24 hours notice and will be from 5:30PM to 7:30PM Mon-Fri.  Can be shown Sat & Sun from 9AM to 7PM, but will still require 24 hour notice.
